rwen]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1571||[[Henry Percy, 8th Earl of Northumberland|Sir Henry Percy]],<br> ''sat for Northumberland and repl. by'' ?|| [[Simon Musgrave|Sir Simon Musgrave]]  <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1572|| [[Simon Musgrave|Sir Simon Musgrave]]|| [[Edward Scrope]],<br> ''died and repl. Nov 1580 by'' [[Thomas Boynton (MP)|Sir Thomas Boynton?]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1584||[[Thomas Scrope, 10th Baron Scrope of Bolton|Thomas Scrope]]|| [[Robert Bowes (diplomat)|Robert Bowes I]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1586||[[Robert Bowes (diplomat)|Robert Bowes I]]|| [[Henry Leigh (MP)|Henry Leigh]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1588/9|| [[Thomas Scrope, 10th Baron Scrope of Bolton|Sir Thomas Scrope]]|| [[Robert Bowes (diplomat)|Robert Bowes I]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1593||[[Nicholas Curwen]]|| [[Wilfred Lawson (died 1632)|Wilfred Lawson]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1597||[[Joseph Pennington (MP)]]|| [[Christopher Pickering (MP)|Christopher Pickering]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1601 (Oct)|| [[William Huddleston (died 1628)|William Huddleston]]|| [[Gerard Lowther (1561\u20131624)|Gerard Lowther II]] <ref name = HoP3/>\n|-\n| 1604\u20131611|| [[Wilfred Lawson (died 1632)|Sir Wilfred Lawson]] || [[Edward Musgrave]]\n|-\n| 1614|| [[Wilfred Lawson (died 1632)|Sir Wilfred Lawson]]||[[Thomas Penruddock|Sir Thomas Penruddock]]  \n|-\n| 1621/2|| [[Sir George Dalston]]|| [[Henry Curwen|Sir Henry Curwen]]\n|-\n| 1624|| [[Sir George Dalston]] ||[[Ferdinando Huddleston]]\n|-\n| 1625|| [[Sir George Dalston]]|| [[Patricius Curwen]]\n|-\n| 1626|| [[Sir George Dalston]] || [[Patricius Curwen]]\n|-\n| 1628|| [[Sir George Dalston]]|| [[Patricius Curwen|Sir Patricius Curwen, Bt]]\n|-\n| 1629-1640|| ''No Parliament summoned ''\n|}\n\n===MPs 1640\u20131832===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Year!!First member!!First party!!Second member!!Second party\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\" |\n|style=\"background-color: {{/meta/color}}\" |\n|[[Short Parli